Enum DatabaseNavigator.Response

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DatabaseNavigator.Response>
Database.DatabaseNavigator.Response

DatabaseNavigator
public static enum DatabaseNavigator.Response
extends java.lang.Enum<DatabaseNavigator.Response>
The list of integers for responses to queries from the control panel or viewer NOTE: This is only used by the viewer and the control panel EXAMPLE OF HOW TO USE: "DatabaseStatements.Response.STORE_BILLBOARD_SCHEDULE.getValue();"
